      <title>瑞银，野村，UniCredit失去了对欧盟债券卡特尔罚款的上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/ubs-nomura-unicredit-lose-bid-to-block-eu-bond-cartel-fines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团AG，Nomura Holdings Inc.和Unicredit Spa未能推翻欧盟反托拉斯的罚款，总计数亿欧元征收了他们在该地区主权债务危机期间与政府债券交易合谋的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/ubs-nomura-unicredit-lose-bid-to-block-eu-bond-cartel-fines</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 08:57:12 GMT</pubDate>
